structure.unit: STATE LIBRARIES -- LIBRARIANS -- STATE ARCHIVES AND RECORDS

law.text: The board shall require a fee of not less than five dollars ($5) nor more than twenty dollars ($20) to be paid by each applicant for a librarian's certificate.
law.history: Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 65, sec. 1, effective June 26, 2007. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4618-130h.
